      <section>
          <h1>Ideas</h1>
          <p>Ideas are public entities in the community. You can view and comment them.<br />Participants and creators can edit their concept and knowledge associated.</p>
          <p>
            <a href="{{ path('i_list_ideas')}}" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
              Show ideas
            </a>
          </p>
      </section>
      <section>
          <h1>Projects</h1>
          <p>Projects have more limited visibility. You can view their public details and comment them.<br />Participants and creators can edit lists, wiki and resources associated.</p>
          <p>
            <a href="{{ path('sp_list_projects')}}" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
              Show projects
            </a>
          </p>
      </section>
<!-- ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ -->
